[Between February and March 2019, Peru reported 2 outbreaks of equine infectious anemia. The outbreaks were located in the departments of Lima and Junin. The event was resolved in May 2019. See event summary and updated map at http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review/viewsummary?reportid=29758.

Maps of Peru can be seen at https://www.nationsonline.org/oneworld/map/peru-political-map.htm and https://www.theonlyperuguide.com/peru-travel-information/maps/peru-map-regions/. - Mod.CRD

